Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Day
    The Day class stores the forecast information for a single day.
    DayPanel
    The DayPanel class displays the forecast information for a single day.
    Deserialize
    Deserializes the data.ser file to load user presets
    GUI
    The GUI class creates and maintains the graphic interface through which the user interacts with the program
    LocalWeather
    The LocalWeather class stores the current forecast information.
    LocalWeatherPanel
    The LocalWeatherPanel class displays the current forecast and weather information
    Location  
    LongTermForecast
    Class LongTermForecast parses the JSON for the long term forecast, initializes all of the Day objects for that data, and stores them in an array.
    LongTermPanel
    This class displays the Long Term Forecast, by creating/containing an array of DayPanel objects
    MakeFont
    Creates new fonts based on a input style representing a font file.
    MarsWeather
    The MarsWeather class stores the current forecast information.
    MarsWeatherPanel
    The MarsWeatherPanel class displays the current Mars weather information
    SavedData
    Structures the saved information
    Serialize
    Serializes the data.ser file to store user presets
    ShortTermForecast
    Class ShortTermForecast parses the JSON for the short term forecast, initializes all of the ThreeHourPeriod objects for that data, and stores them in an array.
    ShortTermPanel
    This class displays the Short Term Forecast, by creating/containing a collection of ThreeHourPanel objects
    ThreeHourPanel
    The ThreeHourPanel class displays the forecast information for a three hour period.
    ThreeHourPeriod
    The ThreeHourPeriod class stores the forecast information for a three hour period.
    WeatherApp
    WeatherApp is the main class for Team 22's weather viewing program.
    WeatherIcon
    Takes an id code integer from OWM and looks up the corresponding hex number to form a new unicode value.
